cdata.name: Insureum
cdata.desc:
Located in South Korea, Insureum is a Blockchain-basedplatform for theinsurance market intervenients. It aims to create an ecosystem where there will be acting three main entities: theInsurance companies, 3rd parties, and the users/policyholders.Insureum's main role is to assist insurance companies inmatching insurance policies with individual lifestyles.

The ISR token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed by the Insureum. Users are expected to be able toutilize the token as a medium of exchange value within the platform's community (providers, developers, and insurance users).
